PROBLEM
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Given an image, obtain the cartoon version (abstraction) of the image using bilateral filtering.

IMAGES : image.jpg

FILES:
assignment8.m = This is the main function that implements the algorithm to catoonize the image.

FUNCTION FILES: 
bilateralFilter.m = This function implements the bilateral filter given the image and the spatial parameter and 
		    range parameter as input argument.

detectEdge.m = This function implements the edge detection on the bilateral filtered image as per the algorithm described 
		in the paper.

quant.m = performs the quantization on the luminance channel of the image.

cartooniza.m = this function performs entire algorithm to cartoonize the image given as input to the function.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

